    • applications.WordTracker

    public class WordTracker
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    WordTracker.java
    Version:
    1.0 Class Description: This class represents a word tracker that process text files, maintain a binary search tree of word information, pringting word reports, and serializing/deserializing the tree.
    Author:
    Jiyeon Heo, Tze-chi Chan, and Parinthorn Songsana

      • serializeTreeToFile

        public void serializeTreeToFile()
        Serializes the wordTree to a binary file for later use. The file is store in the 'res' directory.

      • deserializeTreeFromFile

        public void deserializeTreeFromFile()
        Deserializes the wordTree from a binary file. If the file does not exist, starts with an empty tree. The file is expected to be in the 'res' directory.

        Writes the word report to a text file. The file is stored in the 'res' directory with the given fileName.
        Parameters:
        fileName - The name of the output text file.
